sentence: Looking at units outstanding versus one week prior within the universe of ETFs covered at ETF Channel, the biggest outflow was seen in the ProShares UltraPro QQQ ( TQQQ ), where 1,400,000 units were destroyed, or a 11.5% decrease week over week.
Among the largest underlying components of TQQQ, in morning trading today Apple ( AAPL ) is off about 1.1%, and Microsoft Corporation ( MSFT ) is lower by about 1.3%.

And on a percentage change basis, the ETF with the biggest outflow was the ProShares Ultra Consumer Goods ( UGE ), which lost 75,000 of its units, representing a 33.3% decline in outstanding units compared to the week prior.
Among the largest underlying components of UGE, in morning trading today Procter & Gamble Company ( PG ) is off about 0.4%, and Coca-Cola Company (KO) is lower by about 0.2%.
